vicoop-codex-cli is a TypeScript reimplementation ("language port") of the
OAuth sign-in and LLM-call subset of OpenAI Codex (codex-rs). The upstream
Rust source has been ported and modified. This distribution does NOT include
the upstream terminal UI, so the upstream Ratatui (MIT) attribution carried in
the OpenAI Codex NOTICE does not pertain to this work and is omitted under
Section 4(d) of the Apache License, Version 2.0.

